title: Wednesday, June 24, 2020

So it's been nearly a week since I've begun writing my Daily Notes over at [[Copingmechanism.com]]. I have mixed feelings about it. On one hand, having nearly all my writing in one place is great. On the other hand, I really like creating quick posts and notes here in TiddlyWiki. I'm going to stick with it over there for a while yet, but one never knows where it ends up.